sentences: Cecilia Birgitta Vennersten-Ingemansson (born September 26, 1970, in Gothenburg) is a Swedish pop singer.
Cecilia Vennersten performed the Mariah Carey song Hero at Sikta mot stjärnorna in 1994.
Her first album named Cecilia Vennersten released the same year was a great success in Sweden and Norway.
In 2006 her 3rd album, Under stjärnornas parasoll, was released.
